{"tid":349914,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[JS3349 入咗Poly Food Safety and Technology嘅同學入一入來","createTime":"2017-08-07T01:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T06:02:48.000Z","uid":131143,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"543d44bb3dc04062e30975dc95680b4382598b67","tid":349914,"uid":131143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"話說今日係jupas 放榜嘅大日子<br />\n有冇人入咗JS3349 BSc (Hons) in Food Safety and Technology揮一揮手<br />\n恭喜你成為咗我地FST嘅其中一份子<br />\n收到offer唔好唔記得第一時間交留位費呀<br />\n跟住之後登入PolyU eadmission 登記你個人資料啦<br />\n如果遇到啲乜疑難或者想知道更多有關依科嘅詳請，無任歡迎聯絡我地嘅莊員<br />\n記住要註冊個陣確認做學生會會員，咁樣先可以黎ocamp架<br />\n有咩想問都可以PM我<br />\n想知多D野同我地聯絡資料，可以係FB search&quot;2017-2018 PolyU Food Safety and Technology 食品科技與食物安全 新生揮手區&quot;"},{"pid":"be9e4934143ca96b2a4dfe6782f29a6948c904c5","tid":349914,"uid":83235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"有咩出路介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1530d6dd35593d9118897d85dc74bfa400ffd40","tid":349914,"uid":74538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩出路介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong>成為freestyle之鬼</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f945616f13ead656e73d5f23682de11a4a5d1ea","tid":349914,"uid":83235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩出路介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong>成為freestyle之鬼</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得不行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360ddce2d70b0a4e5f85a49b23e5f76b090a9c2b","tid":349914,"uid":131143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:09:56.000Z","msg"